com.microsoft.bingads
Class AuthorizationData

java.lang.Object
  com.microsoft.bingads.AuthorizationData

public class AuthorizationData
extends Object

Represents a user who intends to access the corresponding customer and account. An instance of this class is required to authenticate with Bing Ads if you are using either ServiceClient or BulkServiceManager.
